Wilayah data (data/wilayah.php)
================================

The file `data/wilayah.php` is **bundled** with this package as compiled PHP
data derived from the Indonesian administrative region project:

  https://github.com/cahyadsn/wilayah

Original work: Copyright (c) cahya dsn; licensed under the MIT License.
See the header in the upstream `db/wilayah.sql` for the full license text.

The compiled PHP file contains only province, regency/kabupaten/kota, and
kecamatan rows (desa/kelurahan are omitted) for use in NIK wilayah validation.
